title: Green Iguana
description: A green iguana resting on a rock. The lizard has a vibrant green body with darker green stripes along its back and tail. Its skin appears textured, and it has a long tail and sharp claws, indicating its adaptation to climbing. The background is blurred, suggesting a natural habitat.

title: Shark Swimming in Ocean
description: A realistic depiction of a shark swimming gracefully in clear blue ocean waters, with sunlight filtering through the surface.

title: Pike Fish
description: A close-up image of a pike fish swimming in clear water, surrounded by aquatic plants. The fish has a long, slender body with a pointed snout and distinctive markings.

title: Purple Starfish on Coral
description: A vibrant purple starfish is resting on a bright green coral surface. The starfish has five elongated arms, and its color contrasts sharply with the lush green background of the coral, creating a striking visual.
